
=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.7 ***
=====================================================================

--> Included MagLED, RedDensGrad, and RoSE to plot.

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.6a ***
=====================================================================

--> Using figlet name.

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.6 ***
=====================================================================

--> Added the molecular electrostatic potential to the properties
      evaluated.

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.5 ***
=====================================================================

Some changes to the help menu and support for long command line
options (e.g. --help, and --version).


=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.4 ***
=====================================================================

 --> Minor spelling corrections
 --> The class wavefunction now correctly reads files with a number
      of primitives equal to a multiple of 20
--> The class bondnetwork foresees the cases where 
      maxBondDist have not been determined due to non of the
      atoms are linked (according to the Van Der Walls sum criteria,
      i.e., the algorithm for drawing CPK/ball&stick molecules)


Known Bugs
    --> The program crashes for the following configuration:
          densline lif.wfn -p L -P -a 1 6
          There is no atom 6, it causes a segmentation fault 11
 

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.3 ***
=====================================================================

 Added the field Magnitude of the Gradient of LOL

Known Bugs
    --> The program crashes for the following configuration:
          densline lif.wfn -p L -P -a 1 6
          There is no atom 6, it causes a segmentation fault 11

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.2 ***
=====================================================================
 
 Minor details added.
  --> The script for gnuplot does not use xterm anymore. Instead
        a direct call is made to plot the image in the pdf file
        (through epstopdf)
  --> In the help menu is stated that epstopdf must be installed
        in the system.

-----------------------------------------------------

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.1 ***
=====================================================================

 Minor details added.
  --> Adds the atom labels in the plot.
  --> Improvings on the help menu.
  --> Activates logscale if the plot property is rho, MagGradRho,
         or KinetEnerG (option -p x, x=={d,g,G})
  --> Improvings of on-screen information

